works.description:
This is Energized Keel which you have to 

bury in all four sides of home. It protects the person from evil spirit,  

black magic and tantra problem. For home security from supernatural powers
 
you can use it. no need to do any worship, only just bury these all four  

keel into all four sides of home at sunday night and cut one lemon and
also  
light one incense stick near every keel in all four sides after that no  
need to do anything. Any spirit, negative energy, spirit and tantra badha 

or black magic spell cannot enter into area where you will bury this item.
 
This is energized with dus mahavidya kawach and mantra, It has strong
power  
to protect home and office or land where you will bury, no need to worry  

about supernatural attacks, negative energy, spirits and evils after this 

item you are 100% protected from supernatural problems.
This item also available free of cost with Sarwa Badha Mukti Kawach
